					<h1>Travel Jadoo</h1>
					<p>Traveljadoo.com is a travel site which allows you to plan a trip anywhere around India, helping you every 
					step of the way. Along with pre-planned itineraries, it also has options to help you tailor-make your own travel 
					itinerary and get price quotations right away!</p>
					<p>Informative as well as clever, it has plenty of useful information on Indian cities and hotels, tips for travellers, 
					and comprehensive rail and airline time-tables as well.</p>
					<p>One of the most interesting features is the <a href="index.cgi?mode=init">Smart Route-finder</a> which will give you 
					transport options to travel from anywhere to anywhere, in the best combinations of road, rail and air travel. 
					Jadoo stands for magic - a magical travel site indeed!</p>
